Deployment workflow for $ARGUMENTS environment:

1. Build the service:
```bash
go build -o service .
```

2. Run health checks:
```bash
./service --health-check
```

3. Deploy to $ARGUMENTS:
```bash
kubectl apply -f k8s/
```

